{#
  future_prediction.md.j2 — render
  `future-prediction/<locale>/future-prediction-YYYYMMDD.md` from
  sourcedata JSON.

  Spec: design/sourcedata-layout.md §Markdown rendered shape (after).

  Inputs (passed by render_future_prediction_md.render_day):
    date_iso         : "YYYY-MM-DD"
    coverage_window  : human-readable string for the window stanza
    locale           : "en" | "ja" | "es" | "fil"
    ai_notice_block  : multi-line string carrying the localized notice
    bridges          : BridgesFile.to_dict() (validation_rows[])
    summary          : optional dict with keys
                         plain_language        — short prose
                         findings              — multi-paragraph prose
                         relation_to_my_preds  — multi-paragraph prose

  External vocabulary (Phase 3):
    "## Validation findings"      — keeps the structured table; renamed
                                    section header.
    "## Bridge"                    — paragraphs that reference predictions
                                    by short_label + ISO date, NEVER by
                                    `Pred ID #N`. NO `Coherence N/5` /
                                    `Remaining gap:` markers in markdown.
    "## Summary (Plain Language)"  — optional
    "## Summary of Findings"       — optional
    "## Relation to My Own Predictions" — optional
-#}
